{"type": "article", "id": 25668, "title": "看图：这里是过去24小时内发生的重要的事", "description": "每天我们都会摘取重要的新闻图片。", "date": "2016-04-19T10:06:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 26417, "name": "熊本地震"}, {"id": 6771, "name": "波士顿马拉松"}, {"id": 11546, "name": "伊丽莎白二世"}], "category": 5, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 72, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606160040yxUtFpsrV6fC5k1i.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>过去的一段时间里，你需要知道的有：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><b>1、继续关注日本熊本地震</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160030is7Pvf1ZHLW8qYp5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Anadolu Agency/Getty Images/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">日本熊本县，警察和陆上自卫队持续在地震灾区进行搜救工作。据统计，目前死者已增至 42 人、9 人下落不明。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160031vYFqWE9QwsJpCfmn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">KAZUHIRO NOGI/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">熊本县南阿苏村，自卫队在一处发生土石流塌方的地点寻找 10 名失去联络的村民。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060616003123qhrj8myAuJRavC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68055556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">JIJI PRESS/视觉中国</p></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">在南阿苏村，一名男子查看灾情时掩住了自己的脸。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>2、耶路撒冷巴士爆炸</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160032PkjSViKDZ31qoH0z.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">THOMAS COEX/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">爆炸现场浓烟滚滚。当地时间 4 月 18 日下午，耶路撒冷南部一辆公共汽车发生爆炸袭击，造成至少 21 人受伤。<b><br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060616003251hDRjwJGpvTa73V.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68611111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">THOMAS COEX/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">当地法医检查汽车的残骸。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>3、波士顿马拉松赛</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160033V0zqadCbvYJ2wnHK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">2016 波士顿马拉松赛即将拉开帷幕，警方加强安保戒备森严。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160033gxap1UM0LDOTInjz.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">民众悬挂爱心头像，悼念波士顿马拉松爆炸案的罹难者。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>4、新西兰总理访华</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160034wPFplI9yhEV7xq8G.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">FRED DUFOUR/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">中国北京，人民大会堂前的仪仗队士兵。国务院总理李克强 18 日下午同到访的新西兰总理约翰·基（John Key）进行会谈。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>5、加沙日常</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160034BuA8hCI3ErMOoxmV.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">MAHMUD HAMS/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">一名巴勒斯坦男子看着窗外经过的哈马斯下属武装部队“卡萨姆旅”。</p>\n<h2>除此之外，这些也值得一看：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><b>1、戴面罩的雕塑</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160035VCbh9p5Kjmtw2HsM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Dan Kitwood/Getty Images/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061600350Up7mGXRI4cfDVkL.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Getty Images/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061600367DYPmSHi9VpRzgan.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Getty Images/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">英国伦敦，“绿色和平组织”示威者为数个知名雕像戴上防毒面具。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>2、汽车部件打造英女王巨像</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160037qDyklQ0AIHJRGrZK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.31481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Matt Alexander/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">完全用汽车部件打造的英国女王伊丽莎白二世的雕像近日亮相英国伦敦。雕像高 3.5 米、宽 2.5 米，由 Kwik Fit 在女王 90 岁生日前打造，以纪念她在二战中担任机修工和司机所做出的贡献。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>3、印度热浪来袭</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160038lJ3RdnG2krybxC9X.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">当地时间 4 月 18 日，印度艾哈迈达巴德（Allahabad）气温升至 40 摄氏度，民众冲凉解暑。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>4、阿曼湾的早晨</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160038z8Z1jqpt9Q2rF6oh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63518519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">阿拉伯联合酋长国渔民在阿曼湾（Oman）拉扯渔网。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>5、德国波恩樱花大道</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160039kXQ0uJSfK1WETiox.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">KARIM SAHIB/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160039AW9a0UHXwfZu5sCi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">KARIM SAHIB/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061600403AL1sf0YlwJEGVCr.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">KARIM SAHIB/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">自 1980 年代种下樱花树之后，德国波恩（Bonn）的这条樱花大道已经成为北威州（North Rhine-Westphalia）的一个热门景点。<br></p>\n\n\n"}